Title: Prevent empty service descriptions from being activated
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1586354477
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

There were some very specific cases which could result in services being
created with empty service descriptions. This could never be activated,
since the cores refused to start. The error handling has been improved to
display a helpful error message in this case.
